snippet: Lawyers for a Russian man charged with hacking into business across the U.S. filed new motions in federal court insisting that they don't have a conflict of interest and should remain on the job....

headline.print_headline: Lawyer for Hacking Suspect Say No Disqualification
headline.main: Lawyer for Hacking Suspect Say No Disqualification

lead_paragraph: Lawyers for a Russian man charged with hacking into business across the U.S. filed new motions in federal court insisting that they don't have a conflict of interest and should remain on the job.
